description: The SFAIS project aims to assist Government to develop and establish a comprehensive FAIS that responds to the needs of Govt for policy and programme planning with a bid to increase and facilitate rehabilitation of the agriculture sector

subproject.description:
Output 1.	Framework of FAIS conceptualized 
Output 2.	Capacity development needs assessed, required training plan prepared and implemented
Output 3.	Equipment procured and installed
Output 4.	An Integrated FAIS established
Output 5.	A system of periodic crop monitoring introduced in pilot areas
subproject.title: Strengthening of Food and Agri

title: Strengthening of Food and Agriculture Information System
